<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فِيهِ مَسَائِلُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأُولَى:</span> عَدَمُ الإِيمَانِ بِجَحْدِ شَيءٍ مِنَ الأَسْمَاءِ وَالصِّفَاتِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِيَةُ:</span> تَفْسِيرُ آيَةِ الرَّعْدِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثَةُ:</span> تَرَكُ التَّحْدِيثِ بِمَا لَا يَفْهَمُ السَّامِعُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الرَّابِعَةُ:</span> ذِكْرُ العِلَّةِ؛ أَنَّهُ يُفْضِي إِلَى تَكْذِيبِ اللهِ وَرَسُولِهِ؛ وَلَو لَمْ يَتَعَمَّدِ المُنْكِرُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الخَامِسَةُ:</span> كَلَامُ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ لِمَنِ اسْتَنْكَرَ شَيئًا مِنْ ذَلِكَ؛ وَأَنَّهُ أَهْلَكَهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>